title: Australia vs India, 3rd Test at Brisbane
description: The third Test match between India and Australia in the ongoing Border-Gavaskar Trophy 2024-25 is set to take place from December 14 to 18, 2024, at the iconic Gabba in Brisbane.

title: Inauguration of President Donald Trump
description: Following his victory over Vice President Kamala Harris in the November 2024 election, Donald Trump is set to be inaugurated for a second, non-consecutive term.

title: UK Local Elections
description: The UK Local Elections on May 1, 2025, will be a significant event, as voters across England choose new local councilors and mayors.

title: 2024 NFL Christmas Games
description: The 2024 NFL Christmas Games, streaming exclusively on Netflix, marking Netflix's debut in live streaming and featuring a halftime performance.

title: 2025 Australian Open
description: The 2025 Australian Open is the first Grand Slam of the year, featuring top tennis players from around the world competing in singles, doubles, and mixed doubles events. The tournament is known for its thrilling matches, extreme heat conditions, and high-energy atmosphere.

title: 2025 General Elections in the Philippines
description: The 2025 General Elections in the Philippines will determine new representatives for the Senate, House of Representatives, and local government positions. These midterm elections will serve as a crucial test for the administration of President Ferdinand 'Bongbong' Marcos Jr. and could influence the country's political landscape leading up to the 2028 presidential race.
